Author: blackjok3r#3181
Content: I wouldnt recommend anyone use my scripts, Luke's are the best ones. I gave him mine early on and he improved them no end. Lucky for us he put them on git. Mine are outdated on git and bad. In the end in went with modifying iguana and komodod directly in the source code to improve performance. Scripts only get u so far. The number 1 "cheat" is to just disable autosplit and use 10% of the default utxos

Author: blackjok3r#3181
Content: Everyone can benifit from my multiple months of performance investigations. I mostly did it so we could scale out with smaller servers rather than my own stats. As you can see I came 9th on SH even tho my node is 2nd or 3rd every day ATM....

Author: blackjok3r#3181
Content: Pro tip: 700 kmd utxo was the default before the locking of utxo chosen was added to help with collisions and double spends. With the locking now in iguana you can run very low numbers. Provided you split every 15 mins or so.
